N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4209.2 - Misrepresentation

State Regulations

Any misrepresentation of a material fact concerning the
record of those entered at the licensed quarter horse racing track shall be
deemed a violation and subject the person or persons responsible therefor to
penalties. Notes
